QuestData.Title: What Lies Within
QuestData.Description: As you lay your hand upon the chest, a faint rumbling can be heard. The sound of grinding movement echoes behind you as the chest begins to shut itself.$B$BSomething is approaching!
QuestData.CompletionText: The chest's lid does not budge.
QuestData.RewardText: The chest now grinds open again, the rest of the antechamber fallen silent.
